resources.string: Join us for a future episode with the brand For The Ummah. In this future episode we will be discussing their journey through their brand creation. Tasneem discusses the hardships that the siblings had to over come to begin their small business

We are so excited for y’all to hear our chat with Mahnoor, creator of @mahnjaandecorates ! Throughout the episode, Mahnoor offers gems of entrepreneurial and life advice. We discuss her journey from working in a toxic environment and realizing her potential/drive for baking and decorating; as well as the importance of networking and her emotional role as a connection between community during quarantine.
